{"tid":143983,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"會唔會請no pay leave去旅行?","createTime":"2017-03-05T05:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T13:44:43.000Z","uid":58810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf565226b1209c33fbb1dcb47ce7648d1e6379d4","tid":143983,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"假設唔夠假用/未做夠一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年已經請左5日no pay，想請多4日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a93eac0ddad0909864e8378ca73895f80c8d7bf","tid":143983,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"想請 但會唔批 <br />\n<br />\n有得請解點解唔請，有錢無命享<br />\n<br />\n好葡萄啲鬼佬一年 一兩個月假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc08d144c668bbf426910200e8587624a48fa6b","tid":143983,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"a42599e5234899fae62cc3b6c9a6bb75d0fcebb9","tid":143983,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想請 但會唔批 <br />\n<br />\n有得請解點解唔請，有錢無命享<br />\n<br />\n好葡萄啲鬼佬一年 一兩個月假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下下都要連埋啲公眾假期先夠去到旅行<br />\n人又多機票又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有工轉我一定玩返一兩月先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab11ffc36d9dc245c6381b6f72a1970a348091cc","tid":143983,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T06:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會</blockquote><br />\n試過請幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想請多次驚大佬唔批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就倒左張機票錢落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ded0f4ed6ffceed76e1d2ac5048503151e8df89","tid":143983,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會</blockquote><br />\n試過請幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想請多次驚大佬唔批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就倒左張機票錢落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家已經請到無哂"},{"pid":"6112118c8669d021ac6f19ab7cc08efc18bb90ed","tid":143983,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:27:35.000Z","msg":"點解唔早D拎假紙？唔睇老闆批咗假先訂機票酒店？<br />\n做唔夠一年，公司pro rata計。例如做夠一年有12日AL，做咗半年只有6日。<br />\n如果唔忙，又唔係好多人放，老闆同上司一般會批。<br />\n大把人放假放突，上司同老闆照批，放多咗嘅假搵日扣NPL。<br />\n你睇下自己公司有冇leave entitlement policy，有D寫明邊幾個月係唔准請假，特別情況除外。"},{"pid":"013d819f95e89c3b341d24750667ed777e55196b","tid":143983,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔早D拎假紙？唔睇老闆批咗假先訂機票酒店？<br />\n做唔夠一年，公司pro rata計。例如做夠一年有12日AL，做咗半年只有6日。<br />\n如果唔忙，又唔係好多人放，老闆同上司一般會批。<br />\n大把人放假放突，上司同老闆照批，放多咗嘅假搵日扣NPL。<br />\n你睇下自己公司有冇leave entitlement policy，有D寫明邊幾個月係唔准請假，特別情況除外。</blockquote><br />\n去個旅行放鬆下都要睇人頭<br />\n做狗真係啱晒你"},{"pid":"8ca36923c2fe90e13a6e972179fec7d5f2a03400","tid":143983,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔早D拎假紙？唔睇老闆批咗假先訂機票酒店？<br />\n做唔夠一年，公司pro rata計。例如做夠一年有12日AL，做咗半年只有6日。<br />\n如果唔忙，又唔係好多人放，老闆同上司一般會批。<br />\n大把人放假放突，上司同老闆照批，放多咗嘅假搵日扣NPL。<br />\n你睇下自己公司有冇leave entitlement policy，有D寫明邊幾個月係唔准請假，特別情況除外。</blockquote><br />\n因為我最近先拎左五日五月既no pay<br />\n依家心郁郁想拎埋九月既<br />\n但五月都未放就拎九月 好似唔係咁好意思<br />\n所以想過左五月先問上司批唔批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n岩岩出黎做野唔太識規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一年得8日AL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該無月份唔放得 新年聖誕呢啲總會唔見八九個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0180e8dd3cd85f74f2844135f9faa21ae7526a","tid":143983,"uid":78826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:13:41.000Z","msg":"試過拎14日no pay去旅行，跟住果個月扣埋機票酒店錢同白做冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b25ebf8b4e3d3c57b6b3947dd286417446d1f6","tid":143983,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"請<br />\n番下工兩個月去次旅行放鬆下<br />\n不知幾開心"},{"pid":"d2752dba4603048691b87072d4f1b8d3e7688046","tid":143983,"uid":80037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"請啊 <br />\n唔批咪射波 <br />\n旅行照去"},{"pid":"18128ec6f5bea3e123419a8a69dc285be571bb5a","tid":143983,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過拎14日no pay去旅行，跟住果個月扣埋機票酒店錢同白做冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />14日<br />\n樓又供唔起 小朋友又養唔起<br />\n真係拎啲錢去旅行開心下好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa69368fcb2f0ce69ba1e393997299b753ee17d2","tid":143983,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請啊 <br />\n唔批咪射波 <br />\n旅行照去</blockquote><br />\n射波炒硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大公司"},{"pid":"3083c05ba620b0110e311def2051192e883bd8ee","tid":143983,"uid":78826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過拎14日no pay去旅行，跟住果個月扣埋機票酒店錢同白做冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />14日<br />\n樓又供唔起 小朋友又養唔起<br />\n真係拎啲錢去旅行開心下好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最緊要自己開心姐 如果唔係咁大負擔既 去玩下放鬆一下真係幾好"},{"pid":"f8ff888d9cf2ac8ef74d4d6573c6675dc6af5332","tid":143983,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過拎14日no pay去旅行，跟住果個月扣埋機票酒店錢同白做冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />14日<br />\n樓又供唔起 小朋友又養唔起<br />\n真係拎啲錢去旅行開心下好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最緊要自己開心姐 如果唔係咁大負擔既 去玩下放鬆一下真係幾好</blockquote><br />\n無負擔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一既煩惱就係冇假囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08be80f654b5282d14fd0d304e71980ad0417bc","tid":143983,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T06:42:35.000Z","msg":"會, 唔批就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c6d09b5e1b57042eb1dcb3ddcb8dc28c19e2ea","tid":143983,"uid":4008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:37:58.000Z","msg":"返左幾個月話要去半個月旅行，批左半個月no pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08e8741746427a10d91a4ae395938afb41cd141","tid":143983,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:39:19.000Z","msg":"得8日既西工你斬做"},{"pid":"c32d186dbe68543c671d7f18be1ece4c808dbf50","tid":143983,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:44:23.000Z","msg":"政府工請假有壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a533cef297d30aa2097873c9f10e8781567456","tid":143983,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔早D拎假紙？唔睇老闆批咗假先訂機票酒店？<br />\n做唔夠一年，公司pro rata計。例如做夠一年有12日AL，做咗半年只有6日。<br />\n如果唔忙，又唔係好多人放，老闆同上司一般會批。<br />\n大把人放假放突，上司同老闆照批，放多咗嘅假搵日扣NPL。<br />\n你睇下自己公司有冇leave entitlement policy，有D寫明邊幾個月係唔准請假，特別情況除外。</blockquote><br />\n去個旅行放鬆下都要睇人頭<br />\n做狗真係啱晒你</blockquote><br />\n老細唔批你可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10間入面8間都係咁"},{"pid":"5eef4108d158ac4abec2f03896a0dde4a6db2cff","tid":143983,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:46:28.000Z","msg":"有16日都唔夠用,<br />\n<br />\n再請NO PAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  NOPAY佢地唔洗比錢一定比放"},{"pid":"a90574597cbb9a6f03e97f356cd325e24ca1aaa7","tid":143983,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:54:43.000Z","msg":"會 請過4日去日本<br />\n公司on9唔比預支AL<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbf880bc8e6eb7693eb21a7698048051e1bfdc5","tid":143983,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:24:02.000Z","msg":"每個月都射波 要去旅行就no pay<br />\n<br />\n好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1f946b975dc2884d2167ac5674763aece5ca28","tid":143983,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返左幾個月話要去半個月旅行，批左半個月no pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩類型公司?"}]}